  "description": "<p>John Romero is a games writer, director, composer and artist who started the games industry career in 1900. Since then, Romero has been working with Valve Software, SEGA, Bethesda Softworks and id Software. Romero&#39;s first published game was Catacomb Armageddon. Next, John Romero worked on Blackroom taking on the role of director. Afterwards, John Romero worked on Blake Stone: Aliens of Gold developed by Saffire in 1993. The latest work of John Romero was Quake (2021), published in 2021.</p>",
